"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Emma Garfitt is a Partner in the firm’s Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing team. She has over 20 years’ experience in residential property, with particular expertise in the Buy to Let sector. Emma has advised property investors on acquisitions of HMOs and MUFBs, refinancing, and complex portfolio transactions.</p><p>‍</p><p>Emma is the firm’s Learning &amp; Development Manager. She leads training across the Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing team, helping to embed technical excellence, consistency of approach, and best practice in a fast-evolving market.</p><p>‍</p><p>Emma is also responsible for shaping the firm’s overall training and development strategy, overseeing the progression of trainee solicitors and apprentices, supporting colleagues undertaking professional qualifications, and designing the firm’s early-career development framework. Through this, she ensures clear and structured development pathways while helping to nurture the firm’s future talent.</p><p>‍</p><p>Emma began her career in conveyancing before moving into academia in 2004 as a Senior Lecturer in Land and Property Law. During this time, she completed an LL.M in Commercial Property with distinction, co-authored a land law textbook, and published in leading legal journals. She returned to private practice in 2018, joining Moonstone, where she now combines her academic insight with practical expertise.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"expertise-video_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid expertise-video_content\"><div class=\"expertise-video_content-left\"><h2 class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></h2><p class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></p></div><div class=\"expertise-video_content-right\"><div class=\"expertise-image_wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/plugins/Basic/assets/placeholder.60f9b1840c.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image w-dyn-bind-empty\"></div><a href=\"/emma-garfitt#\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox w-inline-block w-dyn-bind-empty w-lightbox\"><img src=\"emma-garfitt.html\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox-image w-dyn-bind-empty\"><div class=\"lightbox-play-icon\"><div class=\"icon-embed-large w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.33301 32C5.33301 17.2724 17.2721 5.33334 31.9997 5.33334C39.0721 5.33334 45.8549 8.14286 50.8559 13.1438C55.8568 18.1448 58.6663 24.9276 58.6663 32C58.6663 46.7276 46.7273 58.6667 31.9997 58.6667C17.2721 58.6667 5.33301 46.7276 5.33301 32ZM27.1198 43.4134L42.6664 33.7067C43.2482 33.3341 43.6001 32.6909 43.6001 32C43.6001 31.3092 43.2482 30.6659 42.6664 30.2934L27.0664 20.5867C26.452 20.1993 25.6758 20.1755 25.0388 20.5244C24.4018 20.8734 24.004 21.5403 23.9998 22.2667V41.7334C23.9912 42.4774 24.3963 43.1647 25.0514 43.5174C25.7065 43.8702 26.5033 43.8301 27.1198 43.4134Z\" fill=\"CurrentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div><div class=\"lightbox_overlay\"></div><script type=\"applicat